<h1>Welcome to Rock Paper Scissors!</h1>
 
<p>To play this game, all you have to do is guess rock, paper, or scissor. If select same as the computer, you WIN. If you guess the <u>random computer selection</u>, you win!</p>
 
<p>Choose carefully... you only get one try!</p>
 
<br/>
 
<h2>Pick a number:<h2>
 
<% (1..5).each do |number| %>
  <%= link_to image_tag("secret_numbers/#{number}.jpeg"), rock_paper_scissor_path(number) %>
<% end %>